{
 "name": "RPlog_Bombers_Over_Etti_IV",
 "title": "Bombers Over Etti IV",
 "summary": "When a squadron of Imperial Scimitar assault bombers launches from the ISD Vanguard and begins an unannounced patrol over Etti IV, port security officer Roark summons CSA Vice-Prex Simone Drake to the Port Security Office. The two watch with mounting unease as the bombers ignore repeated hails, split into elements, and skim suspiciously close to the Authority's patrol craft and the VSD Phoenix before finally claiming a routine patrol and returning to their Star Destroyer. Reviewing the flight-path data, Drake concludes the Imperials almost certainly scanned the CSA fleet to assess its strength, noting that four such bombers carry enough concussion missiles to destroy the Phoenix, and she orders the patrols doubled and the security teams to heightened alert. Interwoven with the standoff, Roark briefs Drake on a defense attorney named Pike who is pressing to visit the imprisoned General Solo before his trial, and Drake agrees the visit can be arranged once Mr. Dillon and proper security allow it. Distrustful of the Empire's agenda, Drake departs to take the matter directly to Dillon.",
